page.title: 05My Life Today
page.content: My name is Kelly Gray.I live in Manorfield Close, Bellinge. I have Rice Krispies for my breakfast. I have no pets. Ihave four people in my family . I get up at 9 o clock and put the television on. I watch Saturday Superstore. My favourite toy is My Little Pony. My favourite animal is a horse. I like to eat beefburgers for my dinner. My mummy is a house wife.My daddy works at shoe shops in London. I am a member of dance club at my school.We do Maths,Writing,English, Handwriting and choosing. There are 32 children in my class.
